us that they did.

00:15:52.684 --> 00:15:55.520
&gt;&gt; Well, that's what we
see on occasion here.

00:15:55.520 --> 00:15:58.489
We definitely see that and to
me, that's nothing but fraud.

00:15:58.489 --> 00:16:01.260
[ ♪♪ ]

